1. Download xampp:
https://www.apachefriends.org/download.html

2. If you use Kali Linux, you can use Apache in xampp to deploy your local website:
sudo /opt/lampp/lampp start
Restart: sudo /opt/lampp/lampp start
Stop: 	 sudo /opt/lampp/lampp stop

3. Open Firefox, text "localhost" and automatically into your website kekeke.

4. Notice: Source off website have to save in /opt/lampp/htdocs folder. To update, delete or create, you have to be root.

